      "html": "<p>\"石蜡烃，1875年，来自 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of butyl \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/butyl\">butyl</a>，烷基烃，源自 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">butyric acid</i>，一种在变质黄油中发酵产生的产物，源自拉丁语 <i class=\"foreign notranslate\">butyrum</i>（参见 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of butter \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/butter\">butter</a>（n.））+化学后缀 <a title=\"Etymology, meaning and definition of -ane \" class=\"crossreference notranslate\" href=\"/cn/word/-ane\">-ane</a>。\"</p>"
